                                    <c:EdtText group="cke-home" key="sign-up-1" context="{!edtContext}" text='
                                       <ol>
                                       <li><strong><a href="request-a-pack">Sign up</a></strong> to host a Cupcake Day and receive your free fundraising kit in the post</li>
                                       <li>Set the date:  Cupcake Day is 14 June, but you can host yours any day that suits you</li>
                                       <li>Decide when and where to host your day: at home, at work, up a mountain… the choice is yours</li>
                                       <li>Start baking and/or get your friends baking for you (or buy cupcakes from the shop – yes, it’s allowed!)</li>
                                       <li>Raise as much ‘dough’ as possible to help beat dementia.</li>
                                       </ol>
                                       </p>'/>
