                                       <li>Posters to help you spread the word</li>
                                       <li>Fundraising ideas and fun games to play on the day</li>
                                       <li>A donation box and Gift Aid form (for the all-important ‘dough’)</li>
                                       <li>Cake toppers and decorations</li>
                                       <li>A selfie-frame to share your creations on social media</li>
                                       <li>Lipsmackingly fab recipes to inspire you.</li>
                                       </ul>
                                       "/>
                                    <c:EdtText group="cke-home" key="block-text-2" context="{!edtContext}" text='<p style="padding-left:15px">You can also download extra materials on our <a href="downloads"><strong>downloads page</strong></a>.</p>'/>
